  "description": "<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities:</strong></p>\n<p>· Report to Project Manager</p>\n<p>· Submission of technical proposal, monitoring of submittals</p>\n<p>· System design, equipment selection &amp; procurement.</p>\n<p>· Attend meetings, interactions and responsibility towards client’s requirement</p>\n<p>· Project planning, site control and execution.</p>\n<p>· Leading project team, meeting objectives and targets.</p>\n<p>· Ensure full compliance with contract specification, terms and conditions.</p>\n<p>· Resolve operational issues and conceptualization of master plan.</p>\n<p>· Progress reporting and claims</p>\n<p>· Any ad-hoc duties assigned</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p>\n<p>· Degree in Mechanical/Environmental Engineering or Equivalent</p>\n<p>· Singaporean/PR</p>\n<p>· 3-5 years site experience</p>\n<p>· Dynamic, self-motivated, proactive, and results-oriented</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Ayyakannu Buvaneswaran , Ministry of Recruiters Pte Ltd , EA: 12C5314, EA Personnel : R1217664</strong></p>",
